name: parser_calc_campaigns
viewQuery:
SELECT
  parser_campaigns.id,
  parser_campaigns.updated as Updated,
  parser_campaigns.`lastParseDate` as Last_parse_date,
  parser_campaigns.status as Status,
  parser_models.`name` as Model,
  parser_models.`userId` as Model_Id,
  ('@' || parser_models.`username`) as Model_tag,
  parser_campaigns.`createdAt`,
  ('https://onlyfans.com/' || parser_models.`username` || '/c' || parser_campaigns.`campaignCode`) as Campaign_link,
  parser_campaigns.`campaignName` as Tracking_name,
  parser_campaigns.`campaignId` as Campaign_id,
  parser_campaigns.`countSubscribers` as Subscribers,
  parser_campaigns.parsed as Parsed,
  parser_campaigns.suspicious as Suspicious,
  parser_campaigns.inboxes as Inboxes,
  parser_campaigns.reads as Reads,
  parser_campaigns.replies as Replies,
  parser_campaigns.`newFans` as New_fans,
  parser_campaigns.`newSpenders` as New_spenders,
  ((ROUND((parser_campaigns.`newFans` * 1.0 / parser_campaigns.`countSubscribers`) * 100, 2)) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Fan,
  ((ROUND((parser_campaigns.`newSpenders` * 1.0 / parser_campaigns.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Spender,
  (CASE
    WHEN parser_campaigns.`reads` >= parser_campaigns.`newFans` THEN (100.00 || ' %')
    ELSE ((ROUND((parser_campaigns.`reads` * 1.0 / parser_campaigns.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) AS Engagement_Rate,
  (CASE
   WHEN parser_campaigns.suspicious >= parser_campaigns.`countSubscribers` THEN (100.00 || '%')
   ELSE ((ROUND((parser_campaigns.suspicious * 1.0 / parser_campaigns.`countSubscribers`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) as Suspicious_Rate,
  ('$' || ROUND(parser_campaigns.`totalSumm`, 2)) as Total_summ
FROM parser_campaigns
LEFT JOIN parser_models ON parser_campaigns.`userId` = parser_models.`userId`
 ORDER BY parser_campaigns.`createdAt` DESC

name: parser_calc_promotions
viewQuery:
SELECT 
  p1.`id`,
  p1.updated as Updated,
  p1.`lastParseDate` as Last_parse_date,
  p1.status as Status,
  parser_models.`name` as Model,
  parser_models.`userId` as Model_Id,
  ('@' || parser_models.`username`) as Model_tag,  
  p1.`promotionId` as Promotion_id,
  p1.`createdAt` as Created_at,
  ('$' || p1.price) as Price,
  p1.type as Type,
  p1.message as Description,
  p1.`claimsCount` as Subscribers,
  p1.parsed as Parsed,
  p1.suspicious as Suspicious,
  (CASE
    WHEN p1.inboxes > p2.inboxes THEN p1.inboxes
    WHEN p2.inboxes ISNULL THEN p1.inboxes
    ELSE p2.inboxes
  END) as Inboxes,
  (CASE
    WHEN p1.reads > p2.reads THEN p1.reads
    WHEN p2.reads ISNULL THEN p1.reads
    ELSE p2.reads
  END) as Reads,
  (CASE
    WHEN p1.replies > p2.replies THEN p1.replies
    WHEN p2.replies ISNULL THEN p1.replies
    ELSE p2.replies
  END) as Replies,
  p1.`newFans` as New_fans,
  p1.`newSpenders` as New_spenders,
  p1.`returnedFans` as Returned_fans,
  p1.`returnedSpenders` as Returned_spenders,
  ((ROUND((p1.`newFans` * 1.0 / p1.`claimsCount`) * 100, 2)) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Fan,
  ((ROUND((p1.`newSpenders` * 1.0 / p1.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Spender,
  (CASE
    WHEN p1.`reads` >= p1.`newFans` THEN (100.00 || '%')
    ELSE ((ROUND((p1.`reads` * 1.0 / p1.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) AS Engagement_Rate,
  (CASE
   WHEN p1.suspicious >= p1.`claimsCount` THEN (100.00 || '%')
   ELSE ((ROUND((p1.suspicious * 1.0 / p1.`claimsCount`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) as Suspicious_Rate,
  ('$' || ROUND(p1.`totalSumm`, 2)) as Total_summ
FROM parser_promotions AS p1
LEFT JOIN parser_promotions AS p2 ON p1.relatedId = p2.promotionId 
LEFT JOIN parser_models ON p1.`userId` = parser_models.`userId`
WHERE
  p1.`promotionId` < p1.`relatedId`
  OR p1.`hasRelatedPromo` IS FALSE
ORDER BY p1.`createdAt` DESC

name: parser_calc_trials
viewQuery:
SELECT 
  parser_trials.`id`,
  parser_trials.updated as Updated,
  parser_trials.`lastParseDate` as Last_parse_date,
  parser_trials.status as Status,  
  parser_models.`name` as Model,
  parser_models.`userId` as Model_Id,
  ('@' || parser_models.`username`) as Model_tag,
  parser_trials.`createdAt` as Created_at,
  parser_trials.url as Trial_link,
  parser_trials.`trialLinkName` as Trial_name,
  parser_trials.`trialId` as Trial_id,
  parser_trials.`claimCounts` as Subscribers,
  parser_trials.parsed as Parsed,
  parser_trials.suspicious as Suspicious,
  parser_trials.`stackers` as Stackers,
  parser_trials.inboxes as Inboxes,
  parser_trials.reads as Reads,
  parser_trials.replies as Replies,
  parser_trials.`newFans` as New_fans,
  parser_trials.`newSpenders` as New_spenders,
  (ROUND((parser_trials.`newFans` * 1.00 / parser_trials.`claimCounts` * 100), 2) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Fan,
  ((ROUND((parser_trials.`newSpenders` * 1.00 / parser_trials.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%') as Conversion_Rate_to_Spender,
  (CASE
    WHEN parser_trials.`reads` >= parser_trials.`newFans` THEN (100.00 || '%')
    ELSE ((ROUND((parser_trials.`reads`  * 1.00 / parser_trials.`newFans`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) AS Engagement_Rate,
  (CASE
   WHEN parser_trials.suspicious >= parser_trials.`claimCounts` THEN (100.00 || '%')
   ELSE ((ROUND((parser_trials.suspicious * 1.0 / parser_trials.`claimCounts`) * 100, 2)) || '%')
  END) as Suspicious_Rate,
  ('$' || ROUND(parser_trials.`totalSumm`, 2)) as Total_summ
FROM parser_trials
LEFT JOIN parser_models ON parser_trials.`userId` = parser_models.`userId`
ORDER BY parser_trials.`createdAt` DESC
